      <title>巴西咖啡出口商在债务谈判中获得宽限期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/brazil-coffee-exporters-granted-grace-period-in-debt-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[蒙特桑托塔瓦雷斯集团 (Montesanto Tavares Group Participações SA) 旗下的巴西咖啡出口商获得 60 天的宽限期，以便与债权人重新协商债务。]]></description>
