      <title>法国农业信贷银行在联合信贷银行收购意向中增持 BPM 股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/credit-agricole-seeks-approval-to-boost-banco-bpm-stake-to-15</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于面临来自意大利联合信贷银行（UniCredit SpA）的收购要约，法国农业信贷银行（Credit Agricole SA）已将其在 Banco BPM SpA 的股份增加至 15.1%。]]></description>
